                     <interp inst="t18490507-1123-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>, stealing 3 bags and 400lbs. weight of sugar, value 9<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18490507-name-365" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18490507-name-365" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
